      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Tough. PATYEP (3) has been plain his last two, but this is winnable for him at best. Led and belted the Maidens by 3.5L three back this track/trip and draws low today with a jockey switch. Worth another chance. ITWASONLYAKISS (1) comes out of the same race where he made progress, finishing 2.5 lengths from the winner, doing his best work late. Gives away a start, but will finish hard. I'M A DREAMER (4) has been mixing trips and form. Tumbles in grade off the last two, and 1300m suits better. Can surprise. MAX ROCK (5) improved a month ago, beaten 2L over 1600m. Come back to a sprint with a 2kg claim and can't be ruled out.",
